### ========================================
###           PRODUCTS ENDPOINTS
### ========================================
### Base URL: {{apiUrl}}/products
### Todos requieren authGuard (cookies de sesión).
### ========================================

### ---------- LIST PRODUCTS ----------
### Lista productos con filtros opcionales.
GET {{apiUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=20&search=&active=true

### ---------- LIST PRODUCTS (con filtro por categoría) ----------
GET {{apiUrl}}/products?category_id={{categoryId}}&page=1&limit=10

### ---------- LIST PRODUCTS (stock bajo) ----------
GET {{apiUrl}}/products?low_stock=true&page=1&limit=20

### ---------- GET PRODUCT BY ID ----------
GET {{apiUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

### ---------- GET PRODUCT BY BARCODE ----------
GET {{apiUrl}}/products/barcode/{{barcode}}

### ---------- CREATE PRODUCT ----------
### Crea un nuevo producto.
POST {{apiUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "barcode": "7501234567890",
  "name": "Coca-Cola 600ml",
  "unit_type": "pieza",
  "unit_quantity": 1,
  "category_id": "{{categoryId}}",
  "price": 25.00,
  "cost": 18.00,
  "tax_rate": 16.00,
  "stock": 100,
  "low_stock_threshold": 10,
  "active": true
}

### ---------- CREATE PRODUCT (sin código de barras) ----------
POST {{apiUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tortas de Harina 100g",
  "price": 15.50,
  "cost": 10.00,
  "tax_rate": 16.00,
  "stock": 50,
  "low_stock_threshold": 5,
  "active": true
}

### ---------- UPDATE PRODUCT ----------
### Actualiza campos específicos de un producto.
PUT {{apiUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 28.00,
  "stock": 120,
  "active": true
}

### ---------- DELETE PRODUCT ----------
### Elimina un producto (borrado suave si el repo lo soporta).
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/products/{{productId}}


### ========================================
###          CATEGORIES ENDPOINTS
### ========================================
### Único endpoint público (sin authGuard).
### ========================================

### ---------- LIST CATEGORIES ----------
GET {{apiUrl}}/categories
